name: BLOCK-T333
configuration_schema:
$schema: http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#
title: BLOCK-T333 configuration
description: Configuration for BLOCK-T333.
type: object
properties:
  exposure_time:
    description: Exposure time at each pointing in the spiral (seconds).
    type: number
    default: 1.0
  filter:
    description: Filter to use.
    type: string
    default: "g_01"
  note:
    description: A descriptive note to be attached to images taken in the spiral
    type: string
    default: ""
